name: Watt's Up?
description:
Your a mysterious robot that just woke up on a strange island. There is no other way to go just up. Talk to the other robots. Figure out what is at the top of the Tower. 

Controls:

move: Left -A    Right-D

Dash: W

interact: E

Jump: Space

exit: Tab

Thanks for viewing this page. 

This game was made by a single college student 

Game was made using Godot 3.5
